OL,3,CWould a drug consumption room in
OL,4,CBelfast help tackle addiction?
OL,6,FThe issue of drug addiction is not
OL,7,Funique to any major city, but how a
OL,8,Fcity tackles the issue is.
OL,10,FBelfast Council recently voted in
OL,11,Ffavour of installing needle disposal
OL,12,Fbins in certain areas of the city.
OL,14,FIn Dublin, the council has gone
OL,15,Ffurther by opening a supervised
OL,16,Finjection facility located at
OL,17,FMerchant's Quay along the River Liffey.
