OL,3,CWould a drug consumption room in
OL,4,CBelfast help tackle addiction?
OL,6,FIt's taken more than ten years of
OL,7,Flobbying, but since December 2024
OL,8,Fthose who are in the grip of addiction
OL,9,Fhave been able to inject using clean
OL,10,Fneedles under medical supervision
OL,11,Fwithout fear of being prosecuted on
OL,12,Fsite.
OL,14,F"Once you come into the supervised
OL,15,Finjection facility you must have drugs
OL,16,Fon you," explained Eddie Mullins, the
OL,17,FCEO of Merchant's Quay.
