OL,3,CWould a drug consumption room in
OL,4,CBelfast help tackle addiction?
OL,6,F"It's a bit of a juxtaposition
OL,7,Fstatement, but we don't allow you to
OL,8,Fcome in if you don't have drugs - you
OL,9,Fcan't come in and buy drugs here."
OL,11,FThe facility has strict rules that
OL,12,Fprohibit anyone from dealing illegal
OL,13,Fsubstances on the premises.
OL,15,FMr Mullins explained: "The person
OL,16,Fcomes into the facility, they will
OL,17,Fshow drugs to the staff member behind
OL,18,Fthe reception counter and once they've
OL,19,Fanswered a few questions then they are
OL,20,Ftaken into the supervised injection
OL,21,Fbooths."
