OL,6,FThe staff have no way of testing the
OL,7,Fdrugs about to consumed on site,
OL,8,Falthough if a service user is willing
OL,9,Fto provide a sample of the substance
OL,10,Fthey intend to take, it can be sent to
OL,11,Fthe HSE (Health and Safety Executive)
OL,12,Ffor "relatively quick" analysis.
OL,14,F"We have conversations with our
OL,15,Fclients about whether they sourced the
OL,16,Fproduct from a reliable supplier,"
OL,17,Fexplained Mr Mullins.
OL,19,F"You get to know the person and we
OL,20,Fhave open and honest conversations
OL,21,Fabout it.
